    <summary>
      <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-101">当进入锁定状态的递归与此锁定的递归策略不兼容时引发的异常。</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="c5cc6-101">The exception that is thrown when recursive entry into a lock is not compatible with the recursion policy for the lock.</span>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-102"><xref:System.Threading.LockRecursionException> 引发原因有多种，其中包括：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-102"><xref:System.Threading.LockRecursionException> is thrown for several reasons, including the following:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-103">如果一个线程尝试输入的实例<xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim>以递归方式，但该实例不支持递归。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-103">If a thread tries to enter an instance of <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> recursively, but the instance does not support recursion.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-104">如果线程尝试进入<xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim>写模式或可升级模式时该线程的锁最初进入读取模式中的实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-104">If a thread tries to enter a <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> instance in write mode or upgradeable mode when the thread initially entered the lock in read mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-105">此类表示潜在的死锁，因此不允许。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-105">This represents a potential deadlock and therefore is not allowed.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-106">如果允许将一个详细级别的递归将超过用于跟踪递归的内部存储计数器的最大值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-106">If allowing one more level of recursion would exceed the maximum value for the internal storage counter used to track recursions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-107">此限制数值很大，因此任何情况下应用程序都不应遇到此情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-107">This limit is so large that applications should never encounter it.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-108">下面的示例演示两个原因<xref:System.Threading.LockRecursionException>时使用<xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-108">The following example shows two causes of <xref:System.Threading.LockRecursionException> when using the <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-109">程序创建<xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim>通过使用默认构造函数，它不允许使用递归。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-109">The program creates a <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> by using the default constructor, which disallows recursion.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-110">然后，程序将启动进入读取模式锁定的线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-110">The program then starts a thread that enters the lock in read mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-111">该线程尝试锁定以递归方式进入读取模式，并捕获产生的异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-111">The thread tries to enter the lock recursively in read mode, and catches the resulting exception.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-112">最后，该线程尝试进入写入模式，可能会造成死锁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-112">Finally, the thread tries to enter write mode, which would create a potential for deadlocks.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c5cc6-113">该线程捕获产生的异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5cc6-113">The thread catches the resulting exception.</span></span>  
  
